		<li id="menu-item-15677" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-15677"><a title="Vlado Hajdinjak" href="https://www.zsss.si/obrazi-sindikata/vlado-hajdinjak/" class="menu-item-arrow"><img src="https://www.zsss.si/wp-content/themes/zsss/img/dropdown-menu-icon.png">Vlado Hajdinjak</a></li>
	</ul>
</li>
	<li id="menu-item-9394" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-has-children menu-item-9394 dropdown"><a title="Moj sindikat" href="https://www.zsss.si/mojsindikat/" class="menu-item-arrow"><img src="https://www.zsss.si/wp-content/themes/zsss/img/dropdown-menu-icon.png">Moj sindikat</a>
