<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-6312" src="https://www.zsss.si/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/zsss-logo.png" alt="" width="143" height="144" srcset="https://www.zsss.si/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/zsss-logo.png 266w, https://www.zsss.si/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/zsss-logo-150x150.png 150w, https://www.zsss.si/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/zsss-logo-107x107.png 107w, https://www.zsss.si/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/zsss-logo-85x85.png 85w" sizes="(max-width: 143px) 100vw, 143px" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Še nisi članica ali član sindikata?</strong></h2>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.zsss.si/vclani-se/zakaj-postati-clan/">Preberi razloge za včlanitev</a>, <a href="https://www.zsss.si/sindikati_zsss_kategorije/sindikati-zsss/">izberi svoj sindikat</a> in <a href="https://www.zsss.si/pristopna-izjava/">se včlani</a>!</h4>
